#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:9
msgid "Sphinxビルド時間の計測手段（timeコマンドとMeasure-Command）"
msgstr ""
"Measurement method for Sphinx build time (time command and Measure-Command)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:11
msgid ""
"Sphinxで多言語サイトを構築・運用していると、ドキュメントビルドの所要時間が徐々に伸びてくることがあります。性能改善の第一歩として重要なのが、 "
"**現状のビルド処理にどの程度時間がかかっているのか** を把握することです。"
msgstr ""
"When building and operating a multilingual site with Sphinx, the time "
"required to build the document may gradually increase. The first step in "
"improving performance is to understand **how much time the current build "
"process is taking**."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:13
msgid "本記事では、Sphinxビルドの処理時間を簡易に測定するための基本的な方法についてまとめます。"
msgstr ""
"This article summarizes the basic method for easily measuring the processing"
" time of Sphinx builds."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:21
msgid "Linux/macOSの場合: ``time`` コマンド"
msgstr "For Linux/macOS: ``time`` command"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:23
msgid ""
"LinuxやmacOSなどのUnix系環境では、以下のように ``time`` "
"コマンドを使うことで、任意のコマンドの実行にかかった時間を簡単に測定できます。"
msgstr ""
"In Unix environments such as Linux and macOS, you can easily measure the "
"time taken to execute any command by using the ``time`` command as shown "
"below."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:29
msgid "実行後に表示される例："
msgstr "Example shown after execution:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:37
msgid "``real`` は実際に経過した時間（壁時計時間）"
msgstr "``real`` is the actual time elapsed (wall clock time)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:38
msgid "``user`` はユーザ空間で使ったCPU時間（Python処理など）"
msgstr "``user`` is the CPU time used in user space (Python processing, etc.)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:39
msgid "``sys`` はシステム空間で使ったCPU時間（ファイルI/Oなど）"
msgstr "``sys`` is the CPU time used in system space (file I/O, etc.)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:41
msgid "この手法は、複雑な準備なしで全体所要時間を知ることができ、最も手軽です。"
msgstr ""
"This method is the easiest and allows you to know the total time required "
"without complicated preparation."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:46
msgid "Windowsの場合: ``Measure-Command`` （PowerShell）"
msgstr "For Windows: ``Measure-Command`` (PowerShell)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:48
msgid ""
"Windows環境では、``time`` コマンドは利用できません。代わりに、PowerShellの ``Measure-Command`` "
"を使って処理時間を計測します。"
msgstr ""
"The ``time`` command is not available in a Windows environment. Instead, use"
" PowerShell's ``Measure-Command`` to measure processing time."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:54
msgid "実行結果の例："
msgstr "Example of execution result:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:60
msgid ""
"このように ``TotalSeconds`` や ``TotalMilliseconds`` の項目で、コマンドの実行にかかった時間を確認できます。"
msgstr ""
"In this way, you can check the time taken to execute a command using the "
"``TotalSeconds`` and ``TotalMilliseconds`` items."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:65
msgid "補足：Pythonコードに計測を埋め込む方法"
msgstr "Supplement: How to embed measurements in Python code"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:67
msgid "OSに依存しない方法として、Pythonコード内で ``time`` モジュールを使って処理時間をログ出力するのも有効です。"
msgstr ""
"As an OS-independent method, it is also effective to log processing time "
"using the ``time`` module in your Python code."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:78
msgid ""
"Sphinxをカスタムコマンドやsetup.pyから呼び出している場合には、こうした計測を埋め込むことで、言語ごとの時間や各処理の詳細も把握できます。"
msgstr ""
"If you are calling Sphinx from a custom command or setup.py, you can embed "
"these measurements to understand the time for each language and the details "
"of each process."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:83
msgid "まとめ"
msgstr "summary"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:85
msgid "Sphinxのような静的サイトジェネレーターでは、処理時間の把握が運用改善の第一歩です。以下の方法を状況に応じて使い分けましょう："
msgstr ""
"For static site generators like Sphinx, understanding the processing time is"
" the first step to improving operations. Use the following methods depending"
" on the situation:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:87
msgid "Linux/macOS： ``time`` コマンド（最も簡単）"
msgstr "Linux/macOS: ``time`` command (easiest)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:88
msgid "Windows： ``Measure-Command`` （PowerShell標準）"
msgstr "Windows: ``Measure-Command`` (PowerShell standard)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:89
msgid "クロスプラットフォーム： Pythonの ``time`` モジュール"
msgstr "Cross-platform: Python's ``time`` module"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-26-sphinx-build-measure-time.rst:91
msgid "今後はこれらの計測結果をもとに、不要なキャッシュの削除や並列ビルドの導入など、段階的な改善へとつなげていく予定です。"
msgstr ""
"In the future, we plan to use these measurement results to make gradual "
"improvements, such as deleting unnecessary caches and introducing parallel "
"builds."

